      "content": "it's probably just anxiety right? i've been really stressed with the trip and the airport was a madhouse. i feel like i can't get enough air but like, if i just sit down and relax it'll go away. u dont think i need to rush to the ER or anything for just some chest tightness and being out of breath, do u?",
